---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Terms of Service — Blissful Butterfly Yoga" description="Terms of service for Blissful Butterfly Yoga classes, yoga therapy sessions, and digital products." noindex={false}>
  <section style="padding:80px 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:680px;">
      <h1 style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,2.8rem);margin-bottom:2rem;">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--color-ink);opacity:0.55;margin-bottom:2rem;">Last updated: April 2025</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem;font-size:0.975rem;line-height:1.8;color:var(--color-ink);opacity:0.8;">
        <p>By booking a class, session, or program with Blissful Butterfly Yoga ("Veronica Carpenter"), you agree to the following terms.</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Health disclaimer</h2>
        <p>Yoga and yoga therapy are complementary practices and are not substitutes for medical care, psychotherapy, or other licensed healthcare services. Always consult a qualified healthcare provider before starting a new movement practice, especially if you have a medical condition or injury.</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Cancellations</h2>
        <p>For livestream classes, please cancel at least 2 hours before class start. For yoga therapy sessions, please give at least 24 hours notice. Late cancellations may result in forfeiture of the session fee.</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Refunds</h2>
        <p>Drop-in classes are non-refundable once attended. Programs and packages are refundable within 7 days of purchase if no sessions have been used. Contact Veronica directly with any concerns.</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:veronica@blissfulbutterflyyoga.com" style="color:var(--color-rose);text-decoration:underline;">veronica@blissfulbutterflyyoga.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
